                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Charleston</placeName>\n                                        <date>12 April 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>My dear friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I have recd several apologies from<lb/> you for\n                                        not writing which are unnecessary as I<lb/> know you have\n                                        been very busy since your return<lb/> I have just learned\n                                        that <persName>Revrd Ellis Lyons</persName> has been<lb/>\n                                                  supoened<add>?</add> to attend a trial of\n                                                  <persName>Rev Henry</persName> vs <persName>I\n                                                  Leeser</persName><lb/> for slander. I had some\n                                        inkling of <del>it but</del> the intention<lb/> but did not\n                                        suppose it would be put in execution,—<lb/>I write now\n                                        merely to suggest that you will keep<lb/> perfectly quiet\n                                        and not commit yourself by any remarks<lb/> in\n                                                  <placeName>Phil<hi rend=\"sup\">a</hi></placeName>.\n                                                  <persName>Mr Lyons</persName> is <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">no</hi> evidence, as <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">you</hi> never<lb/> told\n                                                  <persName>Mr Lyons</persName> any thing about\n                                                  <persName>Mr Henry</persName>, <persName>Mr\n                                                  Lyons</persName><lb/> heard it from a third or\n                                        probably a fourth person<lb/> which is <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >no evidence at all</hi>. I suppose you have<lb/>\n                                        procured counsel &amp; <del>and</del> be guided entirely by\n                                        him.<lb/> I am sorry our good friend\n                                                  <persName>SS.</persName> is not in\n                                                  <placeName>Phila</placeName> as<lb/> he would have\n                                        probably advised you as to how you<lb/> are to proceed. Let\n                                        me know the particulars and if<lb/> I can be of any use to\n                                        you in any way? You<lb/> will have to summon <persName><hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">Dr Raphael</hi></persName> and\n                                        have a<lb/> commission sent to examine the parties in\n                                                  <placeName>Cincinatti</placeName>—<lb/>—your\n                                                  <sic>defence</sic> will be however <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">not to prove</hi> your<lb/>\n                                        remark <hi rend=\"underline\">true</hi>, as the greater the\n                                        truth the greater<lb/> the Libel, but to make <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">him prove</hi> that you said<lb/>\n                                        any thing <hi rend=\"underline\">libellous</hi>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The Occident is at hand and Jerusalem has\n                                        been<lb/> my companion among my leisure hours. I have</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p32f7kb46/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
